   15                                  $\eta_{r} = \left( \frac{1 - \varphi^{\delta}}{\left\lbrack {1 - F\left( {\varphi\varepsilon\gamma} \right)} \right\rbrack^{B{\mathit{Φ}}_{m}}} \right)^{- B{\mathit{Φ}}_{m}}$                                                                                      Costa etal. [2009];
                                        où: $F = \left( {1 - \xi} \right) \cdot \text{erf}\left\lbrack {\frac{\sqrt{\pi}}{2\left( {1 - \xi} \right)}\varphi\left( {1 + \varphi^{\delta}} \right)} \right\rbrack$ et                                                                                 $\varphi = \frac{\phi}{\phi_{m}}$
                         $\eta_{\ast} = \eta\left( {\mathit{Φ}}_{m} \right) = 2\left\lbrack {1 - \left( {1 - \xi} \right)\text{erf}\left( \frac{\sqrt{\pi}}{\left( {1 - \xi} \right)} \right)} \right\rbrack^{- B{\mathit{Φ}}_{m}}$                    

